"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:34:06.000Z","msg":"錄音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩年代片都冇, 錄音邊有可信性"},{"pid":"d175cd6ad47fadedbb1d48084c70970b8faff3d1","tid":936358,"uid":128568,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:39:35.000Z","msg":"中央成立<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">退役軍人事務部</span></strong>，希望做好退伍軍人信訪工作<br />\n個事務部係負責處理D退伍軍人既訴求定處理D退伍軍人呀?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7555f99c46da22586cebf7296d18c0bc7965bb","tid":936358,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:39:56.000Z","msg":"好似睇緊魔法少女小圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n魔法少女係軍人，退休會變魔女<br />\n<br />\n然後一代軍人打一打軍人<br />\n<br />\n無限循環直至爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f04c06ad05ef22a1389336149f64c577bd5a29e","tid":936358,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:58:03.000Z","msg":"好文重溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【山東財困舉債達11000億】<br />\n【分析員: 重慶、吉林、雲南、湖南數據異常】<br />\n<br />\n山東省上月公布一份省級預算調整方案報告，省政府要求中央政府伸出援手。<br />\n1/. 在目前10238億元舉債限額基礎上，再增加978億債務;<br />\n2/.要求中央向山東省財政補貼額，由491億，再加碼一成至539億;<br />\n<br />\n文件提到，山東省過去一年財政收入減少，支出大幅增加，收支矛盾突出。<br />\n省政府承認，山東省已陷入財政困難的局面。<br />\n<br />\n再細看山東省近年的財政狀況，可以說每下愈況，預算收入和實際支出相差達2800億。<br />\n2014、2015年山東省政府仍然有盈餘，到2016年開始就急促惡化，由2015年的盈餘255億，暴跌到今年頭三季赤字突破一千億，這個赤字跟新增舉債額度相約。<br />\n<br />\n【四省數據真確性被質疑】<br />\n另外，內地海通證券研究員姜超發表分析報告，指出除了早前自曝大幅虛報經濟數據的遼寧、內蒙和天津外，重慶、吉林、雲南、湖南，過去幾年公布的數據亦出現類似的異常情況，主要是一方面經濟增長數據亮麗，但財政收入增幅持續低迷甚至倒退。<br />\n<br />\n#山東財困<br />\n#伸手問中央攞錢<br />\n#舉債<br />\n#有線中國組<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/1612680905543056\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fposts%2F1612680905543056&d=9hmRhwtFAtlAEPAiNVSA8DM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=02a726f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/1612680905543056</a>"},{"pid":"5f2c6284a6d7d1eca6d2b6364834c30a83a6748c","tid":936358,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:03:24.000Z","msg":"東北果邊，D国企長期財困，根本係亂印錢。"},{"pid":"5823c2d7af074d759584c31de75d1c869b444857","tid":936358,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60226b022c4b0bbdbaa85ef17068a51aa935ba23","tid":936358,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c0ad2e03581f55515e5db508aab9de064ef36bc","tid":936358,"uid":89063,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:45:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">頭蓋骨給他們敲碎，一定要把他們照打死，往死裡幹，幹不死就往死裡幹。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617b61d23534ff8f901decdea52b7b17b0b3c63e","tid":936358,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d175cd6ad47fadedbb1d48084c70970b8faff3d1","tid":936358,"uid":128568,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:39:35.000Z","msg":"中央成立<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">退役軍人事務部</span></strong>，希望做好退伍軍人信訪工作<br />\n個事務部係負責處理D退伍軍人既訴求定處理D退伍軍人呀?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:30:49.000Z","msg":"處理哂d退役軍人咪冇訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b985e7e92bf336df6791e8fb7c60d0f7cccab1","tid":936358,"uid":90704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:00:30.000Z","msg":"「總指揮已經說了，我們每人有打狗棒，打死一個算一個，多打死幾個震驚全國。」<br />\n<br />\n總指揮咁撚勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.